snippet.title: Friday Night Funkin' VS Pomni & Jax | The Amazing Digital Circus / FUNKIN (Digitalizing) (FNF Mod)
snippet.description:
Friday Night Funkin' VS Pomni & Jax for the PC in 2160p Ultra HD, but this time we take on Pomni & Jax from The Amazing Digital Circus. I Dan K - Created Music: https://youtu.be/vKDHAV7gcvw
Matias - Created mod: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Tp0PkXQmMLU

Idk if it's a joke song but I love the music and especially Pomni's chromatics. BF is in an abandoned building and out of the blue he sees a hat. Boyfriend decides to wear the hat, but then it transports him to The Amazing Digital Circus where he finds Pomni, and then the song begins. Girlfriend (GF) isn't in the mod.

We'll be playing The Amazing Digital FUNKIN. Can Boyfriend Defeat Pomni?

Friday Night Funkin' : The Amazing Digital FUNKIN:
https://gamebanana.com/mods/478318

Watch the series by GLITCH!
THE AMAZING DIGITAL CIRCUS: PILOT
https://youtu.be/HwAPLk_sQ3w?si=k2gFcuG1ENUp3LLQ

All Songs from Friday Night Funkin' VS Pomni & Jax Mod Timestamp:
00:00 Digitalizing - Song (Pomni vs BF)
01:10 Jax
01:54 Outro - CommunityGame

Mod Creators for VS Pomni & Jax below

https://gamebanana.com/mods/478318
Matias  - sprites and charting
I Dan K - composed the song and the chromatics
Gooseworx - The amazing digital circus
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCqvpFAiRcY96CjKwiGHgwpg
Glitch productions - The amazing digital circus
